Package: r2d1
Title: DBI Client and API Wrapper for Cloudflare D1
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Noam", "Ross", , "noam@raft.foundation", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight DBI-compliant database interface and API client
    for Cloudflare D1, the serverless SQLite database. Provides wrappers
    for all D1 REST API endpoints, including time travel and
    bookmark-based restoration, plus convenience functions for common
    multi-step workflows such as exporting and downloading databases.
